     O* * *                                 ','
     O* * *                    P@JOK7
     O* * *                                 ','
     O* * *                    P@JOK8
     O* * *                                 ','
     O                         P@NAME
     O                                      ','
     O                         W@GOKE
     O                                      ','
     O                         W@3804
     O                                      ','
     O                         W@3347
     O                                      ','
     O                         W@3503
     O                                      ','
     O                         W@3764
     O                                      ','
     O                         W@3931
     O                                      ','
